    public interface Variation
extends org.eclipse.emf.cdo.CDOObject
    A representation of the model object 'Variation'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Type
    • Value Provider
    • Min Value
    • Max Value
    • Max Variations
    • Varied Object Id
    • Name
